      "id": "PopularPost179586",
      "post_content": "Just so we're clear:  \nThere are 20 Troll-type creatures without Hexproof.  \nThere are 2 with hexproof. They are [Troll Ascetic](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Troll Ascetic) and [Thrun, the Last Troll](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Thrun, the Last Troll) -- who is also an ascetic.  \n  \nWizards also owns the D&D brand, and let me tell you-trolls are easy to target with [Fireball](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fireball)s and [Lightning Bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt)s.",
      "posted_by": "Askthespartan",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost179586\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Just so we're clear:<br/>There are 20 Troll-type creatures without Hexproof.<br/>There are 2 with hexproof. They are <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Troll Ascetic\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Troll Ascetic\">Troll Ascetic</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Thrun, the Last Troll\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Thrun, the Last Troll\">Thrun, the Last Troll</a> -- who is also an ascetic.<br/><br/>Wizards also owns the D&amp;D brand, and let me tell you-trolls are easy to target with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fireball\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fireball\">Fireball</a>s and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lightning Bolt\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt\">Lightning Bolt</a>s.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '179586'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy47590\">Askthespartan</span>\r\n                                (7/16/2011 9:29:26 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\